{"tid":1073724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜: 中聯辦主任和我進行了「情感交流」","createTime":"2019-03-23T02:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T08:55:48.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"44c641b69ca5653512afb915b7a79c2d5e7f0d8a","tid":1073724,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:05:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2736100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2736100&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD11QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=554af161\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2736100&h=85d3f556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2736100</a><br />\n<br />\n證實與中聯辦主任吃晚餐 韓國瑜：純粹情感交流<br />\n2019-03-22 23:00<br />\n<br />\n〔記者王榮祥／高雄報導〕高雄市長韓國瑜今晚向隨行媒體證實，與香港中央駐港聯絡辦公室（中聯辦）主任王志民一起吃晚飯，他強調純粹是情感交流、也互相打氣，認為香港與高雄間應更增加交往頻率，互相之間多來多往，是溫馨而有感情的交流。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜進一步指出，兩人用餐間的談話，純粹是就高雄與香港間應多往來，王志民認為過去往來太少、很可惜，他認為香港可提供高雄更多發展機會、做生意的機會，韓國瑜說，王志民對此說法也很認同，雙方都感覺氣氛非常融洽。<br />\n<br />\n現場媒體追問韓國瑜，訪中聯辦被認為有政治意涵，與先前訴求的經貿之旅好像就有點不同？<br />\n<br />\n此外，香港泛民派人士、前立法會議員及香港眾志創會主席羅冠聰直指韓王見面，這是「魔鬼的交易」。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜則表示，第一點、尊重香港本地政府一切安排，第二點，他在高雄選舉時講得非常清楚，高雄的未來只有朋友、沒有敵人，只有道路、沒有圍牆，所有香港政府的安排，只要時間允許，都欣然接受。<br />\n<br />\n他說，歪嘴雞不需要挑米吃，所有對我們伸出溫暖的手，我們都當成好朋友，至於香港內部有甚麼不同看法，是喜歡也好，不喜歡也好，意見不一樣等等，讓香港內部自己去處理，我們完全尊重，對高雄的未來，只有道路沒有圍牆，所有四面八方的好朋友願意歡迎高雄，都是我們的好朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/xUzpTbi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUzpTbi.jpg&h=2b84a62a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58c9286b80513732c3aa9441c1c7862fd44368e1","tid":1073724,"uid":26752,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff5b65876330947b625eab9a4fc992e50dfc45e","tid":1073724,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45200e255073bbd03315d82f9e435e3de7d530ac","tid":1073724,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"神交"},{"pid":"1a7c117cd275f25f8f6bdda3772b78284eab67b4","tid":1073724,"uid":47674,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"全晚任飲吾倆液<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f4b8577c9068c50d3637f51281c80a3145a158","tid":1073724,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:25:43.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜個樣，成個智障咁樣"},{"pid":"469dd7e8f302e46bd09d6b46795ebead597750bf","tid":1073724,"uid":48088,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/of7CtRO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fof7CtRO.jpg&h=5d41b6b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a648b6788a7d91f7eecc8d8d97f5c31d16dc6751","tid":1073724,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:55:26.000Z","msg":"真係唔明高雄人點解揀佢"},{"pid":"9461926eb9d8fd0fc4deacded8ccc0930f7d5014","tid":1073724,"uid":47674,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a648b6788a7d91f7eecc8d8d97f5c31d16dc6751","tid":1073724,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:55:26.000Z","msg":"真係唔明高雄人點解揀佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:12:39.000Z","msg":"一個地方嘅人如果有智慧 早就發咗達啦"},{"pid":"b41b08b08e2d173d3c40ff4bc6f2ccd06faa44fe","tid":1073724,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQXxITt5ewDi9L-zEnplC6RTuUPL1CVNsE_1TJo7S3BeC-I1H6i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2F